{"actor":{"type":"human"},"content":{"blocks":[{"content":"1\t# Conversation Ledger\n2\t\n3\tDurable, attributable records of visible coding-agent conversations.\n4\t\n5\tConversation Ledger is the neutral foundation of a small ecosystem:\n6\t\n7\t- `conversation-ledger` stores normalized, provenance-preserving conversation evidence.\n8\t- `turnbridge` records and transfers visible conversations between coding CLIs.\n9\t- `intent-recall` later retrieves evidence to help agents reason about original and superseded intent.\n10\t\n11\tThis repository is intentionally at the design stage. It has no released API yet.\n12\t\n13\tSee [product intent](docs/PRODUCT_INTENT.md) and the [WIP technical design](docs/WIP_TECHNICAL_DESIGN.md).\n14\t\n15\t## License\n16\t\n17\t[MIT](LICENSE)\n18\t","tool_use_id":"toolu_01AKh86fs5RJH3kCaXi559gL","type":"tool_result"}],"role":"user"},"context":{"cwd":"/Users/evintunador/repos/evintunador/conversation-ledger","dirty_fingerprint":"e12e6fe04f3a78e3a5f3ff041be237d2a899e1d55f1148de6f18442622160697","repo":"conversation-ledger"},"conversation":{"id":"claude-code:700cd82f-2f79-4cd6-b727-0f81230e0837","seq":19},"id":"ev1-bef48383ab00f83578ef7fe340891add864b09db7d9859234a1ad078f059ee60","kind":"conversation_turn","occurred_at":"2026-07-18T22:12:12.971Z","producer":{"session_id":"700cd82f-2f79-4cd6-b727-0f81230e0837","source":"claude-code","tool":"cledger","version":"0.1.0"},"raw":{"data":{"cwd":"/Users/evintunador/repos/evintunador/conversation-ledger","entrypoint":"cli","gitBranch":"main","isSidechain":false,"message":{"content":[{"content":"1\t# Conversation Ledger\n2\t\n3\tDurable, attributable records of visible coding-agent conversations.\n4\t\n5\tConversation Ledger is the neutral foundation of a small ecosystem:\n6\t\n7\t- `conversation-ledger` stores normalized, provenance-preserving conversation evidence.\n8\t- `turnbridge` records and transfers visible conversations between coding CLIs.\n9\t- `intent-recall` later retrieves evidence 